Toshiba Bidding to Acquire Smart-Meter Company Landis+Gyr, Nikkei Says

-- B y   S t e v e n   M c P h e r s o n
-- 
2011-05-09T17:11:49Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-09/toshiba-bidding-to-acquire-smart-meter-company-landis-gyr-nikkei-says.html
Toshiba Corp. (6502)  is bidding against U.S.
and European companies to acquire smart-meter maker Landis+Gyr,
the Nikkei newspaper reported. The winning bid may reach the
equivalent of 200 billion yen ($2.5 billion), the report said.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Steven McPherson at 
 smcpherson@bloomberg.net  